{"tid":2195492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人權組織向巴赫發信要求收回北京2022年冬奧主辦權","createTime":"2020-09-09T08:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T08:21:44.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"36e8ce554453e2cf53ae2649b970608f9329f586","tid":2195492,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"人權組織向國際奧委會主席巴赫發信，要求收回北京2022年冬季奧運會主辦權。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱代表西藏、新疆維吾爾族人及香港的人權組織代表，趁國際奧委會在瑞士召開會議前向巴赫發信，指責北京在2008年主辦夏季奧運後，人權記錄未有改善，並進一步建立監察網，囚禁維吾爾族人，又在香港及內蒙古侵犯人權，向台灣作出威嚇。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548693-20200909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548693-20200909.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=f60019d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548693-20200909.htm&h=46f00c23\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548693-20200909.htm</a>"}]}